overview:
Over 50 year back the vision and compassion of our Grand Father Vidya Ras Raj, Late Shri Kanhey Lalji and our Father Late Dr. Phoolchandji Patni gave birth to the legacy of caring for the deprived masses. He combined in a very unique formula grater vision with vast knowledge of the most ancient system of ayurvedic medicines. The result of his untiring effort is an array of over 50 unique preparations formulated to teeate the common ailments and provide efficacy and safety.

GOMTESH is a GMP certified company with a ultra modern plant being loyal to this legacy, since then Gomtesh Laoratoies has been manufacturing Ayurvedic patent and proprietary medicines for ailing masses.

Gomtesh Laoratoies, adopts a positive attitude towards a modern style of business practice. Highly qualified and specialized persons are involved in the day to day growth of gomtesh lab. The key to the efficiency of our product is the modern method of qualitative analysis. This goes towards more efficient standardization of active ingredient in every product.
